y of Bedfordshire<\/a>, who provided invaluable technical support for the team throughout the sessions. Their details can be found <a title=\"University of Bedfordshire students\" href=\"http:\/\/www.mirandanet.org.uk\/researchexchange\/events\/mirandanet-bett12-programme-11th-14th-january-london\/workshop-sessions-at-bett12\/university-of-bedfordshire-students\/\">here<\/a>.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Tony Parkin has written an extremely useful account of the morning&#8217;s events. You can read it here:\u00a0Empowering students to harness the power of social networking for learning Using MindMeister The interactions in the MirandaMod and the FlashMeeting are further augmented &hellip; <a href=\"https:\/\/www.mirandanet.org.uk\/mirandamods\/mirandamods-at-bett\/bett12\/empowering-students-to-harness-the-power-of-social-networking-for-learning\/\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&rarr;<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":0,"parent":44,"menu_order":3,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.mirandanet.org.uk\/mirandamods\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/119"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.mirandanet.org.uk\/mirandamods\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.mirandanet.org.uk\/mirandamods\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.mirandanet.org.uk\/mirandamods\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.mirandanet.org.uk\/mirandamods\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=119"}],"version-history":[{"count":7,"href":"https:\/\/www.mirandanet.org.uk\/mirandamods\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/119\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":248,"href":"https:\/\/www.mirandanet.org.uk\/mirandamods\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/119\/revisions\/248"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.mirandanet.org.uk\/mirandamods\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/44"